{"search_data": "PunjabPunjab Ayushman Bharat Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana for Farmers [Free Health Insurance Scheme]Punjab govt. starts Ayushman Bharat Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana for farmers, kisan can avail free treatment of Rs. 5 lakh in any govt. / empanelled private hospitals under AB-SSY health insurance schemePunjab Ayushman Bharat Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana for FarmersPunjab Mandi Board has started Ayushman Bharat \u2013 Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana for all farmers of the state. This AB-SSBY is a state specific health insurance scheme in which farmers can avail cashless treatment of Rs. 5 lakh. Already registered farmers should contact the market committee offices for the following purposes:-Verification of names of farmers.To get e-cards.To get names of family members added.Information regarding government hospitals.Information regarding private hospitals.All the farmers who want to avail Punjab Ayushman Bharat Sarbat Sehat Bima Yojana for Farmers should contact their respective market committee offices. Farmers needs to fill application form and carry supporting documents like J Form / Sugarcane Weight Slip.Farmers can visit the official website at shapunjab.in or mandiboard.nic.in. They can now apply for AB-SSY Scheme to get their name enrolled in the list of beneficiaries.This scheme is functional for other category people of the state for which the hospital list & beneficiary list is still available at the official website. Similar to the process for other people, farmers also needs to get their e-cards prepared to avail cashless treatment at hospitals.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/ludhiana/punjab-govt-starts-free-health-insurance-scheme-for-farmers/articleshow/74479840.cms  at  "}